data.description: Welcome to this beautiful well maintained, one level,  move in ready home. This house offers 3 bedrooms and two bathrooms with plenty of space. Bathrooms COMPLETE REMODEL, newer roof, water heater, indoor and outdoor fresh paint, new electric range. Amazing fenced backyard paradise with fruit trees , covered outdoor area, playground and space for RV and Boat . Nice front yard landscaping. This is a great home. Call your agent now and hurry on to take a look.
